data.title: Faith-Based Initiative
data.meta_description: The City partners with the Faith-Based Community with a clear focus on helping those most in need. Read more about the Faith-Based Initiative.
data.text:
Improving Lives

Improving the lives of families and communities most in need through:

collaborations based on relationship

partnerships that are engaged
